entries.femaleVariant: OK, I know Hal's secure, but let's not pretend it went smoothly. I expected you to be more professional, V.
Nicely done – Hal's very happy, talks about you non-stop. Only good things, of course.
Please, no more stunts like that in the future. Closing the gig.
And remember, V – word gets around. Closing the gig.
Hal's dead, V. Tried to make it out on his own, but that poor girl with cyberpsychosis got to him first.
That was the fate you left him to when you abandoned him. I won't forget this.
